title: Kendall Jenner, Gigi Hadid, & Karlie Kloss Walk the Balmain x H&M Runway!
text: Kendall Jenner , Gigi Hadid, and Karlie Kloss strut their stuff while walking the runway during the Balmain x H&M fashion show on Tuesday (October 20) at 23 Wall Street in New York City.
